                     <interp inst="t18191027-73-person850" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was sent for, took the prisoner up stairs, searched her, and found the duplicate of the scarf, pledged that day for 15 s. On coming down stairs Smith's brother found the watch, which 
